Cisco NPUG Docker

Live demo of using docker to build the presentation

git clone npug
cd /project/npug
vagrant up
vagrant ssh
sudo su -
docker images (Should have just the base images listed)
cd landslide && docker build -t yarnhoj/landslide .
cd nginx && docker build -t yarnhoj/nginx .
docker run -it -d -name app -v /var/www/html yarnhoj/landslide
docker run -it -d -name web --volumes-from app -p 80:8000 yarnhoj/nginx
super + 3; super + r google-chrome
localhost:8000/presentation.html

